channel.title: Not to sure what this means any ideas?
channel.description:
is it my jdk ? or just my java? but someone help?[code]Error: Registry key 'Software\JavaSoft\Java Runtime Environment'\CurrentVersion'
has value '1.8', but '1.7' is required. Error: could not find java.dll Error: Could not find Java SE Runtime Environment. Press any key to continue . . .[/code]
